<h1><%= WEB_NAME %>账户重设密码</h1>

<p>重设密码请点击如下链接:</p>

<a href="<%= url_for controller: 'user', action: 'password_reset', activation_token: @student.reset_token, email: @student.email, only_path: false %>">
  <%= url_for controller: 'user', action: 'reset_token', activation_token: @student.reset_token, email: @student.email, only_path: false %></a>

<p style="color: #B00100"><strong>本链接将于一小时后失效</strong></p>

<p>如果你不想重置密码，请忽视这封邮件，您的密码将保持不变</p>
